## Welcome
Hi!

## Discord
I've worked on many projects on discord including [an all-around utility bot](https://github.com/jagrosh/Spectra), an [auto-moderator bot](https://github.com/jagrosh/Vortex), a [downloadable music bot](https://github.com/jagrosh/Spectra-Music), and a [simple cleverbot](https://github.com/jagrosh/FrostCleverbot), among other things. 

## Other Projects
I've developed a [small text-parsing language](https://github.com/jagrosh/JagTag) that can be easily expanded.
